@startuml
title 土质分类检测（复杂度 O(n³)）

actor 分析员 as user
participant "前端" as front
participant "Gateway" as gw
participant "zrws-analyze" as svc
participant "Python AI" as ai
database "MySQL" as db
database "Redis" as cache
queue "RabbitMQ" as mq

== AI 推理流程 ==
user -> front: 提交分析请求
front -> gw: POST /api/v1/analysis/soil
gw -> svc: 转发
svc -> db: [SQL] SELECT t_soil_sample WHERE mission_id=1024
svc -> ai: [gRPC] classifySoil(spectral_data)
ai -> ai: 光谱特征提取 + CNN 分类
ai --> svc: SoilClassificationResult
svc -> db: [SQL] INSERT t_analysis_result
svc -> mq: 发送 analysis.completed
svc --> gw: R<AnalysisResultVO>
gw --> front: 分类结果 + 置信度
front -> front: ECharts 饼图 + 热力图

== 异常流程 ==
alt AI 超时
    ai -[#red]-> svc: 30s 超时
    svc -> svc: Sentinel 熔断降级
    svc --> gw: 503 FALLBACK
    gw --> front: 系统繁忙，稍后重试
else 样本不足
    svc --> gw: 400 样本数量不足（需≥10）
    gw --> front: 提示补充样本
end

@enduml
